---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';
---

<Layout title="Code Documentation | check_ptr_validname">
  <main>
    <Section fullWidthBorder index source="check_ptr_validname.c">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>Code Documentation</h2>
        <p>
          <code>check_ptr_validname.c</code> is a single-binary C implementation focused on predictable monitoring behavior and minimal runtime dependencies.
        </p>

        <h3>Main Flow</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Parse CLI options into a runtime options struct.</li>
          <li>Validate IP and choose resolver.</li>
          <li>Execute PTR lookup and measure lookup latency.</li>
          <li>Validate returned hostname with strict rules and optional IDN checks.</li>
          <li>Perform forward lookup and verify forward-confirm match.</li>
          <li>Map result to Nagios/Icinga state and emit text or JSON output.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Key Data Structures</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><code>struct options</code>: parsed runtime flags and timeout/resolver behavior.</li>
          <li><code>struct check_result</code>: state, details, latency, and per-check booleans.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Output Modes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Human-readable monitoring line with optional perfdata.</li>
          <li>Machine-readable JSON mode via <code>--json</code>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Build Layout</h3>
        <pre><code>make
make OS=linux ARCH=x86_64
make OS=windows ARCH=x86_64 CROSS=x86_64-w64-mingw32-
</code></pre>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout>
